    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "A really appealing, honest classic in good condition that offers the kind of driver-quality charm many buyers are after. It presents well, has a clean overall look, and should be easy to enjoy right away, while still showing the light age and use you\u2019d expect from a well-kept vintage car rather than a fully restored showpiece. If you want a solid, attractive classic with plenty of character and without the top-tier price tag, this is a great one to consider.",
