      "description": "Exceptionally well-kept mint-condition example that presents beautifully throughout and should appeal to buyers looking for a standout car rather than just a usable driver. The paint, trim, glass, and interior all show extremely well, with the kind of clean, cared-for appearance you hope to find in a top-tier example. It has clearly been maintained with pride, and buyers can expect a highly presentable, impressive car that is ready to enjoy.",
