      "description": "Solid fair-condition car that appears to be a usable driver, but it shows its age and is not a perfect example. Expect visible cosmetic wear, older paint and trim, and the kind of blemishes, interior wear, and general aging you\u2019d expect from a car that has been used rather than fully restored. It should appeal to someone looking for an honest driver they can enjoy and improve over time, rather than a collector-grade car. Priced accordingly for its condition.",
